description:
In this episode, Pastor Gary Kent interviews Dr. Neil Nedley and talked about the impact of anxiety, stress, and depression in our day-to-day life, especially during the COVID-19 Pandemic. Stress and anxiety affect almost every one of us at some point in our lives, often keeping us awake at night with tense muscles and a racing mind. Is there a way out of this cycle that seems to never end? In this episode, you will meet a Doctor who is changing peoples lives through out-of-the-box methods that may surprise you!
